<h2 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h2>

<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>1</td>
      <td>pkt</td>
      <td>Edgell Instant Mashed Potatoes</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>2</td>
      <td>cups</td>
      <td>boiling water</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2 id="method">Method</h2>
<p>Slowly add boiling water to mashed potato powder while stirring.</p>

<p>Stand for 1 minute.</p>

<p>Sit down and eat it.</p>

<h3 id="hot-tip">Hot tip</h3>
<p>I added some butter and pepper.</p>
